name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) As always a 10 for this site. I love to go and eat a good hamburger, well done and to the point that I like. It is a wonder. Still waiting to try the smoked meats. The truth is that the most faithful to the authentic American.

(Original)

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) American food restaurant with smoked meats that I have already been to several times and the truth is that it never disappoints. It has a wide variety of starters, burgers and meats. On this occasion we have tried the nachos with chili, a combo of meats (chicken, Creole sausage and ribs) with two sides and a hamburger and a couple of cakes for dessert. Everything is delicious and as you can see in the photos the quantities are generous, so I recommend going very hungry.
The attention of the waiters is very good, I hope to return soon and continue trying things on the menu.

(Original)
Restaurante de comida americana de carnes ahumadas que ya he venido en varias ocasiones y la verdad que nunca defrauda. Tiene gran variedad de entrantes, hamburguesas y carnes. En esta ocasion hemos probado los nachos con chili, un combo de carnes(pollo, salchicha criolla y costillas) con dos acompañamientos y una hamburguesa y de postre un par de tartas. Todo esta buenisimo y como se puede ver en las fotos las cantidades son generosas, con lo que recomiendo ir con mucha hambre.
La atencion de los camareros es muy buena espero pronto volver y seguir probando cosas de la carta.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The place is very well decorated. We ordered some very tasty chicken wings with spicy barbecue sauce and very good hamburgers too. I give it 4 stars because the macncheese that I ordered as an accompaniment were reheated in the microwave (the bowl was hotter than the food itself). It's a shame about this detail because the rest was worth it.

Le pongo 4 estrellas porque los macncheese que pedí de acompañamiento se notaban recalentados en el microondas (el bol venía más caliente que la propia comida) una pena este detalle porque el resto merecía la pena.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
Good beer (Brewdog). Good sides. Good food in general.
Hamburger: The patty (meat) is very good much better than most places in the city. I really liked it and this is the most important part. The bread (second most important part), is soft and fluffy which is nice, however, since it's a regular brioche bread, it's very sweet and steals all that good taste from the patty. I would order burger again, but with a less sweet bread, maybe potato buns something like that.
But everything in general is good. I'll come back.

Two drinks and two main courses (with sides) is around 35€-45€.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Very well decorated place, very American, the best: the croquettes and the Red Velvet, the worst: the rest, the somewhat bland normal Mac&cheese, the hamburgers with very pressed meat "looked like they were from the supermarket", the very brisquet, not even with sauce it had fix, the ribs with too much sauce flavor, the wings too much sauce and dry.
It gave the feeling that the product was overheated, prices too high for the quality delivered, friendly and attentive staff, and just because of the staff, I do not give it two stars, if they do not change it is 100 times better than some Foster Hollywood and they are much more cheap, the truth is that after seeing some youtubers, we left very disappointed, I will not return unless these errors are corrected, as I said, a brisquet should not be dry and the pullet pork turned into a ball.

P.S. The Pepsi or Coca cola, please much less watered down, thanks 😉

(Original)
Sitio muy bien decorado, muy americano, lo mejor: las croquetas y el Red Velvet, lo peor: el resto, los Mac&cheese normalitos algo sosos, las hamburguesas con la carne muy prensada "parecían de supermercado", el brisquet sequisimo, ni con salsa tenía arreglo, las costillas con demasiado sabor a salsa, las alitas demasiada salsa y resecas.
Dio la sensación de que el producto era recalentado, precios demasiado altos para la calidad entregada, el personal simpático y atento, y justo por el personal, no le pongo dos estrellas, si no cambian es 100 veces mejor algunos Foster Hollywood y son mucho más baratos, la verdad después de ver algunos youtubers, salimos muy decepcionados, no volveré a menos que corrijan estos fallos, lo dicho un brisquet no debe estar reseco y el pullet pork se hacía bola.

PD. La Pepsi o Coca cola, por favor mucho menos aguada, gracias 😉

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We went to eat during the week 4 people, and we played at € 20 per person. We ordered croquettes for starters which were delicious. I ordered the "Wild West" burger, and I was very surprised. It melted in the mouth and tasted brutal. The accompanying potatoes are very good (the cheese topping is a sauce type, it is not very there and they do not add much).
I would recommend it without a doubt, and if the occasion arises I will go again.

(Original)

Se deshacía en la boca y tenía un sabor brutal. Las patatas de acompañamiento están buenísimas (el topping de queso es tipo salsa, no está muy allá y no echan mucha cantidad).
Lo recomendaría sin duda, y si surge la ocasión volveré a ir.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We were there yesterday, Wednesday, July 20, and first we asked if there were foods for people with gluten intolerance. And to my surprise, being a restaurant with such a name and located on a street with so many visitors. They told me nooo, because the food was cross-contaminated. Well, it seemed to me that with the few people there were in the restaurant, or with how easy it is to clean the griddle to make a hamburger, that's little desire to work. To all those people with intolerances and allergies to some food, you have to complain, that cannot be allowed. All you need is desire, gloves, a clean pan, and the customer leaves happy. It's not complicated at all, you just need to like your job. Cheers

(Original)
Estubimos ayer, miercoles 20 de julio, y primeramente consultamos, si habían alimentos para personas con intolerancia al gluten. Y para mi sorpresa, siendo un restaurante con tanto nombre y situado en una calle con tantos visitantes. Me digeron que nooo, por tener contaminación cruzada los alimentos. Pues me pareció que con la poca gente que había en el restaurante, o con lo sencillo que es limpiar la plancha para hacer una hamburguesa, eso es pocas ganas de trabajar. A todas esas personas con intolerancias y alergias a algun alimento, hay que quejarse, eso no se puede permitir. Solo se necesitan ganas, guantes, una sarten limpia, y el cliente se va feliz. No es nada complicado, solo hace falta que te guste tu trabajo. Saludos
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Dozens of celiac clients eat/dine without any problem in our restaurant. In 100% of the cases we warn of a possible cross contamination since it is our obligation and it is for the good of our clients.

At the time you demanded that the iron be cleaned and that way the contamination would end, and it is not like that. This is understood as a lack of training on the subject that we DO have.

Therefore, anyone who can eat with a little cross contamination can enjoy our dishes, otherwise we sincerely do not recommend it.

(Original)
Decenas de clientes celíacos comen/cenan sin problema en nuestro restaurante. En el 100% de los casos avisamos de una posible contaminación cruzada ya que es nuestra obligación y es por el bien de nuestros clientes.

Al momento exigiste que se limpiara la plancha y que de esa forma se acabaría la contaminación, y no es así. Se entiende por ello una falta de formación sobre el tema que nosotros SI tenemos.

Por lo cual, cualquiera que pueda comer con un poco de contaminación cruzada podrá disfrutar de nuestros platos, sino sinceramente no lo recomendamos.

(Translated by Google) Spectacular. Enter my top 3 Burgers in Barcelona. I ordered the largest of all thinking, as always, that it would have too many flavors and I wouldn't like it as much (but I always try them because the quantities lose me). I was very surprised by the quality of the meat and the "simplicity" of the flavors, but in the end, the simple is always the best, and in this case it was. In fact, I tried 2 more, the Chicago and the other I don't remember, and without a doubt the big one was the best.

Pedí la más grande de todas pensando, como siempre, que tendría demasiados sabores y no me gustaría tanto (pero siempre las pruebo porque me pierden las cantidades). Me sorprendió muchísimo por la calidad de la carne y la "simpleza" de sabores pero al final lo simple siempre suele ser lo mejor y en este caso así fue. De hecho, probé otras 2 más, la Chicago y la otra no la recuerdo, y sin duda la grandota fue la mejor.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) 😍🍔🍔 I ate many hamburgers and many dishes of this type of food during my life and I can simply say that today it is my top 1 by far.
I ate some wings, some pulled pork arepas, a smoked nutella and strawberry tart
And a burger in which they bring you some gloves, a bowl of melted cheese and one with smoked bacon cut into pieces, eye here is the fun you have to put the cheese on top of the Burger and the bacon, put on the gloves and stain your face with that delight.... If you don't stain yourself, you're not doing it right.
ALL THE MEAT (wings, ribs, pulled pork, Burger meats.....are prepared in SMOKERS OR GRILL) PLUS THE SMOKERS ARE MANUFACTURED BY THEMSELVES 😍😍
BUT IF THIS SEEMED LITTLE....
SOME DAYS OR EVERYONE PREPARE BRISKET... seriously brisket, I couldn't try it because it's over (imagine the number of people who are going to try that food) and those machines in the form of humans that feed us, preparing during the day and night (some literally do early morning shifts) that meat that melts like an ice cream in summer or a piece of butter on a slice of hot bread....
You could not continue talking over and over again putting points in favor and none against this place...
AND TO ONE DO NOT SPEAK ANYTHING ABOUT THE ATTENTION OF THE STAFF WHO WAS BRILLIANT AT ALL TIMES TO ONE HAD A VERY HIGH STRESS DUE TO THE AMOUNT OF PEOPLE WHO CAME TO EAT NON-STOP.
THANK YOU FOR THIS EXPERIENCE 🍔💓💓💓💓

(Original)
😍🍔🍔Comí durante mi vida muchas hamburguesas y muchos platos de este tipo de comida y simplemente puedo decir que a día de hoy es mi top 1 con mucha diferencia.
Me comí unas alitas, unas arepas de pulled pork , una tarta de nutella y fresa ahumadas
Y una hamburguesa en la cual te traen unos guantes, un cuenco de queso fundido y uno con bacon ahumado y cortado en pedazos, ojo aquí está lo divertido tienes que poner el queso encima de la Burger y el bacon ,ponerte los guantes y mancharte la cara con esa  delicia.... Si no te manchas no lo estás haciendo bien.
TODO LA CARNE( las alitas, costillas, el pulled pork , las carnes de la Burger.....se preparan en AHUMADORES O PARRILLA) ADEMÁS LOS AHUMADORES LOS FABRICAN ELLOS 😍😍
PERO SI ESTO PARECÍA POCO....
ALGUNOS DÍAS o TODOS PREPARAR BRISKET... enserio brisket, no lo pude probar por qué se acabó ( imaginar la cantidad de gente que va a probar esa comida) y esas máquinas en forma de humanos  que nos dan de comer, preparando durante día y noche ( literalmente algunos hacen turnos de madrugada) esa carnes que se deshacen como un helado en verano o un trozo de mantequilla en  una rebanada de pan caliente....
No Se podría seguir hablando una y otra vez poniendo puntos a favor y ninguno en contra de este local...
Y A UN NO HABLE NADA DE LA ATENCIÓN DEL PERSONAL QUE EN TODO MOMENTO FUE BRILLANTE A UN TENIDO UN ESTRÉS MUY ALTO POR LA CANTIDAD DE GENTE QUE VENÍA A COMER SIN PARAR .
GRACIAS POR ESTA  EXPERIENCIA 🍔💓💓💓💓

review_text:
Cuina espectacular, tot estava molt bo i les racions abundants. El brisquet, el millor de tot, tenia mil sabors. El servei sempre molt atent i ràpid. L’únic però, si és que n’hi ha, poder millorar una mica la ventilació, ja que es notava una mica de fum a l’ambient, però ja dic poder, ja que pel tipus de restaurant és lo normal.
Tornaré segur, i molt recomanable sense cap mena de dubte pels amants de les bbq.
Com a curiositat, em va sorprendre que tinguessin en exposició, fumadors a la venda, per als que s’atreveixin a anar una mica més enllà de les típiques bbq de carbó o llenya i preparin les seves pròpies carns fumades

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We arrived on a Saturday without having reserved a table, luckily after 15 minutes a very friendly waiter gave us a place to eat.

We ordered some croquettes for starters:
1. Brisket croquettes, very sweet, soft and caramelized, was the favorite of the table.

2. Rib croquette, it was also creamy and had a caramelized aftertaste, totally recommended but not as good food as brisket.

We ordered a combo of 3 pieces of meat and two appetizers:

Appetizers: Mac & cheese highly recommended, we regret not ordering another extra plate. The potatoes were a house special, but it wasn't for nothing.

The ribs of the combo fell off the bone by themselves and melted in your mouth, highly recommended.

The brisket costs an extra €2.90 and it wasn't that big of a deal either, but we were excited to try it.

To finish we ate some chicken fingers, nothing recommended. The ones you make at home are better.

For dessert we ate a lotus cheesecake, to my liking it had too much gelatin and was very curdled, but the taste of the table loved it.

The price was €50.10 + 20% tip (optional) it is worth going, I recommend it.

(Original)
Llegamos un sábado sin haber reservado mesa, por suerte a los 15 minutos en camarero muy amable nos facilitó un hueco para poder comer.

Pedimos unas croquetas de entrante:
1. Croquetas de brisket, muy meloso, suave y caramelizado, fue la preferida de la mesa.

2. Croqueta de costilla, también era cremosa y tenía un regusto caramelizado, totalmente recomendada pero no tan buena comida la de brisket.

Pedimos un combo de 3 piezas de carne y dos aperitivos:

Aperitivos: Mac&cheese súper recomendado, nos arrepentimos de no haber pedido otro plato extra. Las patatas eran especiales de la casa, pero no era para nada.

Las costillas del combo se salían solas del hueso y se deshacía en la boca, súper recomendadas.

El brisket cuesta un extra de 2,90€ tampoco era para tanto, pero nos hacía ilusión probarlo.

Para acabar comimos unos fingers de pollo, nada recomendado. Son mejores las que uno se hace en casa.

De postre comimos un cheesecake de lotus, a mi gusto llevaba demasiada gelatina y estaba muy cuajado, pero al gusto de la mesa les encantó.

El precio fue de 50.10€ + 20% de propina (optativa) merece la pena ir, lo recomiendo.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
Edito en junio 2022
Por desgracia, ya no es lo que era. Han bajado bastante la calidad de la carne. El local está petado de turistas, la música es demasiado alta da ganas irte de allí más rápido posible.
Los precios siguen siendo asequibles y atención al cliente amable.

Fuimos a este restaurante después de ver los vídeos de unos foodbloggers en youtube. La verdad es que este sitio no nos decepcionó. El local es grande, amplio, decorado estilo Texas. Hemos pedido ensalada César de pollo y hamburguesas Houston y king Ranch. La carne (hamburguesa, bacon, pulled pork) está muy buena, tiene sabor original ahumado. No se puede probar una carne así en otras hamburgueserías. Las porciones son grandes y vienen con un acompañante a elegir: patatas fritas, puré, mac'n'cheese y algo más (no recuerdo). Los precios no son caros para esta calidad y cantidad de comida. En general todo está bastante bien. Si viene algún amigo estadounidense a Barcelona, le llevaría a este sitio.

We got the Swiss cowboy burger and the Wild West burger.
They tasted good, but we had to wait over 40 minutes for our simple burgers.
The place was excellently decorated for Halloween 🎃 👻💀 even the waiter was dressed in costume.
It’s a little overpriced.
They had nice WiFi and a nice outdoor seating area.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Impressive quantity and quality of burgers! Undoubtedly one of the best hamburger restaurants in Barcelona.
I loved the flavor of the meat , with a touch of grilled meat that was not lost despite the extra ingredients and sauces .
In addition, the size of the hamburgers is enormous, the quality, quantity and price ratio is very good.
The super Cheezy was very good and so that you don't get dirty with all the cheese it has, they give you some gloves to eat it, which is a detail and helps you enjoy it much more.
The service very attentive and fast.
The spacious place, very well decorated and in full truth. In short, everything is perfect.

(Original)
Impresionante cantidad y calidad de las hamburguesas ! Sin duda una de las mejores hamburgueserías de Barcelona.
El sabor de la carne me encantó , con un toque a brasa que a pesar de los ingredientes extra y las salsas no se perdía .
Además el tamaño de las hamburguesas es enorme , muy bien la relación calidad, cantidad y precio.
La super Cheezy estaba muy buena y para que no te manches con todo el queso que lleva te dan unos guantes para que te la comas , lo cual es un detalle y ayuda a disfrutarla mucho más
El servicio muy atento y rápido.
El local amplio, muy bien decorado y en pleno cierto . En definitiva todo perfecto .

El servicio es bueno pero tardan mucho porque se suele llenar mucho, pero la espera vale la pena la verdad!
Seguro volveremos, precio medio de hamburguesa con acompañañte (patatas fritas, mac'n cheese o ensalada) unos 15-20eur.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) First I want to explain why I give it one star. Two years ago I went and the meat that melted in the mouth was wonderful, the quantities were so large that I had to ask them to take it away, an exquisite flavor all fresh. But two years ago weeks I went and there is my God! The biggest disappointment tiny amounts, zero taste, the worst soft drink I've ever had in my life was a mixture of water, sugar and turmeric and without gas (supposedly it was the orange ones), I had a rash on my hands when I left (I want to be fair and say that the attention was not bad) it has made me very sad, I don't think it will come back but it would be nice if they went back to their beginnings. I don't know if they change owners or they have decided to make cuts in everything

Primero quiero explicar porque le doy una estrella .hace dos años fui y era una maravilla la carne que se deshacía en la boca ,las cantidades tan grandes que tenía que pedir que me lo pusieran para llevar ,un sabor exquisito todo fresco .pero hace dos semanas fui y !hay dios mío! La mayor de las decepciones minúsculas cantidades ,cero sabor ,el refresco más malo que e tomado en mi vida era una mezcla de agua azúcar y cúrcuma y sin gas(supuestamente era las de naranja),tuve una erupción en las manos al salir (quiero ser justa y decir que la atención no estuvo mal) me ha dado mucha pena ,no creo que vuelva pero si estaría bien que volvieran a sus inicios .no sé si cambio de dueño o han decidido hacer recortes en todo
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Hi Cachita,

Thank you very much for your honest opinion. The truth is that we are the same family owners and both we and our clients think that we have improved a lot since our beginnings. The truth is that I don't know what could have happened.

We take these opinions as very positive because they help us improve, but for this we would like to talk to you and find out what you ordered and where the problem was. Would you be so kind as to write to hola.theranch@gmail.com so we can talk to you?

All the best!

(Original)
Hola Cachita,

Muchas gracias por tu sincera opinión. La verdad es que somos los mismos dueños familiares y, tanto nosotros como nuestros clientes, opinan que hemos mejorando muchisimo desde nuestros inicios. La verdad es que no se qué puede haber pasado.

Estas opiniones las tomamos como muy positivas porque nos ayudan a mejorar, pero para ello nos gustaría hablar contigo y saber qué pediste y dónde estuvo el problema. Serías tan amable de escribirnos a hola.theranch@gmail.com para poder hablar contigo?

Un saludo!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) I'm leaving with a good experience but I think it can be improved. The food is very tasty (and extremely abundant, that is, be careful when ordering because you may not be able to finish it later), also somewhat expensive but good quality/price ratio. The service is good but could be improved. It shows that they have a lot of very young people with little experience. When we entered we were attended by a Latin girl (just like me) and she began to speak to us in English, when I told her that I spoke Spanish it was like she was blocked and made us speak to another person. I don't know if he didn't speak Spanish or what, but being in Barcelona the way to receive someone shouldn't be English by default. Then there was a lot of chaos with the staff, like they were going above and beyond their capabilities. I also want to make it clear that we were always treated with kindness and the service was fast. If they are a little more organized and the staff gain a little more experience, I would give it five stars. We will repeat.

(Original)
Me voy con una buena experiencia pero creo que se puede mejorar. La comida es muy rica (y extremadamente cuantiosa, osea que cuidado al pedir que luego puede que no te la puedas acabar), también algo cara pero buena relación calidad/precio. El servicio es bueno pero mejorable. Se nota que tienen mucha gente muy joven y con poca experiencia. Cuando entramos nos atendió una chica latina (al igual que yo) y nos empezó a hablar en inglés, cuando le dije que hablaba español es como que se quedó bloqueada y nos hizo hablar con otra persona. No sé si es que no hablaba español o que, pero estando en Barcelona la forma de recibir a alguien no debería ser inglés por defecto. Luego se veía mucho caos con el personal, como que iban por encima de sus capacidades. Igual quiero dejar claro que siempre nos trataron con amabilidad y el servicio fue rápido. Con que estén un poco más organizados y que el personal coja algo más de experiencia le daría cinco estrellas. Repetiremos.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We went to dinner at The Ranch restaurant, with the pre-conceived idea that it would be just another "Burger King".

Fortunately, nothing is further from reality. In an environment with a decoration reminiscent of more than one movie that we have been able to see, we tried first of all one of the best Nachos we have ever eaten, delicious.

Later we tried several of the hamburgers, which in addition to very original recipes, were made with high quality meat, and with very, very decent portions for the hungriest.

In short, Quality, Innovation, good atmosphere, and excellent service.

Recommended to go, and repeat.

(Original)
Fuimos a cenar al restaurante The Ranch, con la idea pre-concebida de que sería un "Burger King" más.

Afortunadamente, nada más lejos de la realidad. En un entorno con una decoración que recuerda a más de una película que hayamos podido ver, probamos en primer lugar uno de los mejores Nachos que hayamos comido, riquísimo.

Posteriormente probamos diversas de las hamburguesas, que además de recetas muy originales, eran hechas con carne de gran calidad, y con unas raciones muy muy decentes para los más hambrientos.

En resumen, Calidad, Innovación, buen ambiente, y un servicio excelente.

Recomendado ir, y repetir.

The problem is it took almost 10 minutes before we could sit down and they had 20 empty tables. It reminded me of the "clubs" in America that leave you waiting just to make you wait (terrible marketing).
It occurred to me to protest and the waiter suggested that I leave the place. I would have left but my daughter and I had been going to the hospital for 20 days and we were so tired that we didn't want to leave. Food on the verge of pretty good. But if they don't treat me with respect, I won't come back (even if it's the fault of a rude waiter).

Llegas y tienen un letrero de esperar a que el personal vaya por ti y te siente. El problema es pasaron casi 10 minutos antes de poder sentarnos y tenían 20 mesas vacías. Me recordó a los “antros” de America que te dejan esperando solo por hacerte esperar (pésimo marketing).
Se me ocurrió protestar y el camarero me sugirió que me fuera del lugar. Me hubiera ido pero mi hija y yo llevamos 20 días yendo al hospital y estábamos tan cansadas que ya no quisimos irnos. La comida tirándole a bastante buena. Pero a mi si no me tratan con respeto, no regreso (aun cuando sea culpa de un camarero maleducado).

owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Thanks for your honest answer Sara.

Unfortunately (or fortune) we make the brisket for Friday and, although we make more and more forecast, we run out of stock on Friday.

Understand that it is a meat that is smoked for 24 hours and we perform a specific night shift for it.

As for the pulled pork, we serve it without BBQ sauce so that the client can then serve himself to his liking with any of our 4 sauces.

(Original)
Gracias por tu sincera respuesta Sara.

Por desgracia (o fortuna) el brisket lo hacemos de cara al Viernes y, aunque cada vez hacemos más y más previsión, nos quedamos sin existencias el mismo Viernes.

Comprende que es una carne que se ahuma durante 24 horas y realizamos un turno de noche especifico para ello.

En cuanto al pulled pork lo servimos sin salsa BBQ para que luego el cliente se sirva a su gusto con cualquiera de nuestras 4 salsas.

A recommendation. Next time please, make a reservation, here or wherever you go dinner in Barcelona.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text: Found this great bbq steak n burger restaurant in the city centre.  Very American although all the staff were locals.  It’s the perfect place if u really like your meat and a beer. Wine selection is limited to colours. We had the chicken and avocado burger, and the beef skirt steak. Both with fries and slaw. My steak was slightly undercooked in parts but to be fair this was due to its varying thickness. My partners burger was “awesome” in size and taste. Fries with skin on - also very tasty. Neither of us left hungry and we only had mains. Portions are big and prices quite  reasonable. You can go for the double and triple burgers but you really need to have a massive capacity to finish them. Some of the promo videos playing at the restaurant’s entrance, showing these Uber burgers, dripping with sauce, is enough to put you off.  If it doesn’t then this is defo the place for you.

The place is amazing with background music that transports you to the USA and there is a very good atmosphere for eating quietly. All the staff was very friendly and super fast service!

We will repeat for sure!

El local es una pasada con musica ambiente que te transporta a USA y hay un muy buen ambiente tanto para comer tranquilamente. Todo el staff fue muy amable y un servicio super rápido!

Repetiremos seguro!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) I went in because I was passing through the center, but I was hungry and was pleasantly surprised. I ordered the Longhorn and it was very very rich with meat that you can tell is made on the grill. Perhaps as a point of improvement I would expand the beer menu, with that they would have me there quite permanently.

(Original)
Entré porque estaba de paso por el centro, pero con hambre y quedé gratamente sorprendido. Pedí la Longhorn y muy muy rica con carne que se nota es hecha a la parrilla. Tal vez como punto de mejora ampliaría la carta de cervezas, con eso me tendrían allí bastante fijo.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text: For an american restaurant, it serves as American restaurant!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The menu is wonderful, they have dishes that attract a lot of attention but when served the food is terrible. The food has no American flavor anywhere.

(Original)
El menú es maravilloso, tienen platos que llaman mucho la atención pero al servirla la comida es malísima. La comida no tiene sabor americano en ningún lado.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The burger can be customized to be totally vegan or vegetarian and there is a lot of different food and you get really full. The photos are the nachos and King Ranch.

(Original)
La hamburguesa se puede personalizar para que sea totalmente vegana o vegetariana y hay mucha cantidad de comida distinta y te llenas muchísimo. Las fotos son los nachos y King Ranch.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We were there on 02/13/22 in the evening. Unfortunately we hadn't made a reservation, but the friendly staff assigned us a seat in front of the restaurant. Food was very, very good and served quickly. 2 beers, 1 salad and 2 burgers for just 38 euros. A very good value for money. We recommend.

(Original)
Wir waren am 13.02.22 am Abend dort. Leider hatten wir nicht reserviert, bekamen aber vom freundlichen Personal einen Sitzplatz vor dem Lokal zugewiesen. Essen war sehr, sehr gut und wurde schnell serviert. 2 Bier, 1 Salat und 2 Burger für gerade mal 38 Euro. Ein sehr gutes Preis-Leistungsverhältnis. Sehr zu empfehlen.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text: It is a great place to eat. The food is tasty and authentic. The smoked meat was exquisite, very juicy and delicious. The desert is the cherry on the top :) I definitely recommend it.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
Misleading, this is not a bbq joint it’s basically a steak house. Brisket only available few days a week or maybe once a week(according to waiter, was rude initially too) Salad came out as sautéed veggies, stir fried almost. Only 1 star I give because the beef patty for burger is ok , other than that is MISLEADING
I edited my review for the real truthful now since I read how the owner responded, was trying not to be so harsh
owner_answer: sorry for your experience Sabrina. Brisket is exclusive for Friday to Sunday, please, understand it is a 24 hour preparation meat as is the time it is being smoked. We can't manage to serve it everyday with a high quality.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The food is spectacular, very good attention in a very pleasant atmosphere

(Original)
La comida es espectacular, muy buena atención en un ambiente muy agradable

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Maybe I had high expectations or I was the most crowded day, but I don't think I'll do it again. The food was acceptable (it did not remind me of southern American cuisine at all. See photo of the supposed smoked chicken) and the service was not enough. At 3:00 p.m. They had run out of desserts...
"Flat". Nothing to highlight...

(Original)
Quizá tenía una expectativa alta o fui el día más masificado, pero no creo que repita. La comida aceptable (no me recordó en nada a la cocina sureña americana. Ver foto del supuesto pollo ahumado) y el servicio no daba a basto. A las 15h. Se les habían terminado los postres...
"Plano". Nada a destacar...
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Alfonso, thank you for your honest review.

Excuse us for the comment, but the chicken breast falls under the "Grilled" section, those meats are not smoked. Our specialty is the smoked meats that you could find on the menu.

I recommend you try our ribs and our pulled pork! And if you're here on a Friday night and Saturday, our Brisket.

We hope you can give us another chance. Thanks!

(Original)
Alfons, gracias por tu sincera reseña.

Discúlpanos el comentario, pero la pechuga de pollo entra en la sección de “A la parrilla”, esas carnes no son ahumadas. Nuestra especialidad son las carnes ahumadas que podías encontrar en carta.

Te recomiendo probar nuestras ribs y nuestro pulled pork! Y si estas por aquí un Viernes noche y Sábado, nuestro Brisket.

Esperamos que puedas darnos otra oportunidad. Gracias!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) It is a very nice and cozy place, fast and efficient service. A very varied and attractive menu. However, the food was cold (the meat in the hamburgers, the steak and the fries) and when I say cold I mean cold at all. The drink is quite expensive in terms of soft drinks. Quality - Price is expensive and disappointing.

(Original)
Es un local muy bonito y acojedor, servicio rapido y eficiente. Una carta bastante variada y atractiva. Sin em bargo, la comida estaba fria (la carne de las hamburguesas, la carne steak y las patatas fritas) y cuando digo fria es fria del todo. La bebida pica bastante de precio en tema refrescos. Calidad - Precio es caro y decepcionante.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Till, thank you for your honest response.

Of course we will investigate the fact that the food was cold, excuse us because it is not normal. In any case, please inform the waiter next time and we will solve it by repeating the dishes.

In terms of price, I think we are in a good range with an average ticket of €20.

We hope you can give us another chance!

(Original)
Till, gracias por tu sincera respuesta.

Desde luego indagaremos en el hecho de que la comida estuviera fría, discúlpanos porque no es normal. De todos modos por favor la próxima vez informa al camarero y lo solucionaremos repitiendo los platos.

En cuanto a precio creo que estamos en un buen rango con un ticket medio de 20€.

¡Esperamos que puedas darnos otra oportunidad!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We came with high expectations, and we left completely delighted. Without a doubt, we will return.

(Original)

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Bad behavior of the staff specially with Arabs customers and I get very bad racism in the staff's to Arabs!!
I do not recommend visiting it for this reason, as they deliberately create problems with Arabs customers !!!!

The restaurant workers are making problems with the Arab customers, rude and unfair treatment!

I do not recommend visiting the restaurant and I hope the staff in it improve their behavior!

(Original)
Bad behavior of the staff specially with Arabs customers and I get very bad racism in the staff's to arabs !!
I do not recommend visiting it for this reason, as they deliberately create problems with Arabs customers !!!!

العاملين بالمطعم يصتنعون المشاكل مع الزبائن العرب ، تعامل فظ ومجحف !

لا أنصح بزيارة المطعم واتمنى على العاملين فيه تحسين سلوكهم!
owner_answer:
Dr.Saleh, sorry for the inconvenience.

We know your frustration, but you refused to wear your mask as it is (by the moment) mandatory by law. The team asked you several times to wear it and you refused. We can’t accept that, not from an Arab person, neither a local, neither a German, nobody.

We have two Arab people in our staff and we love them as we do to the rest of the team. Our waiters staff is almost full of Philippine amazing guys. We’re so racist… Even we ordered pizzas and paid for them for our team to enjoy them after a successful day.

As you are mad for asking you to wear your mask several times I think you enjoyed your meal, as you both order Mojitos several times, a full King Ranch, and our Onion Rings. So, your 1 star review is only based in your frustration (I think) for asking you ti wear your mask.

You sent an email and an IG message with the same review. I think you believe you were writing to a great CEO who would fire the restaurant manager for it. This is a family restaurant and I (the owner) was there doing supporting tasks to make the service more fluent, as it was a really busy day.

Of course we apologize if that (yellow haired waiter), as you mentioned in the email talked you in not a really polite way. We were full and running a 65 tables restaurant and had no time to discuss about wearing mask or not after asking it several times.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) A place different from the others, where you can enjoy excellent meat, we had not tried smoked meat and the truth is, it is highly recommended, in addition to having received excellent treatment from all the staff, especially from Nicolás, a very kind, respectful and friendly boy. He recommended the Brisket meat, and it was a very good choice.

(Original)
Un lugar diferente a los demás, donde poder disfrutar de una carne excelente, no habíamos probado la carne ahumada y la verdad, es super recomendable, además de haber recibido un trato excelente por parte de todo el personal, en especial por parte de Nicolás, un chico muy amable, respetuoso y simpático. Nos recomendó la carne Brisket, y fue una elección acertadísima.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Alex, thank you very much for your comment. Nico saw the review and was very grateful. We'll keep it up, thanks!

(Original)
Alex muchisimas gracias por tu comentario. Nico vió la reseña y se sintió muy agradecido. ¡Seguiremos así, gracias!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) A place out of 10, we are from Seville and whenever we travel to Barcelona for business we stop there. The spectacular food and the unbeatable treatment of the owner, we had a small mishap with the reservation, it was a detail without the least importance but even so the owner at the end of the meal addressed us to apologize, that in very few places they do and It is appreciated, without a doubt we will continue to come every time we travel to Barcelona and if you have the opportunity to go we recommend the potatoes au gratin with ranchera sauce and the amount of quality meat they have.

(Original)
Un lugar de 10, somos de sevilla y siempre que viajamos por negocios a Barcelona nos paramos allí. La comida  espectacular y el trato del dueño inmejorable, tuvimos un pequeño percance con la reserva, fue un detalle sin la mínima importancia pero aun así el propietario al finalizar la comida se dirigió a nosotros para pedirnos disculpas, eso en muy pocos sitios lo hacen y es de agradecer, sin duda seguiremos viniendo cada vez que viajemos a Barcelona y si tenéis la oportunidad de ir os recomendamos las patatas gratinadas con salsa ranchera y la cantidad de carnes de calidad que tienen.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Thank you very much guys! We always stand up for everything and I'm glad you value it. We wait for you!

(Original)
¡Muchisimas gracias chicos! Siempre damos la cara por todo y me alegro que lo valoréis. ¡Os esperamos!

review_text: Very nice food and staff. A safe bet if you are not an adventurous eater. The whole place is typical of an American steak/burger place. No complaints here, but is not very authentic if that is what you like.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) I drank a cook without a mask, the waiters didn't rinse with the dishes but we also waited almost 1 hour for the food to be brought to us ... we didn't eat badly but I don't think the truth comes back, oh and it's an expensive place.

(Original)
Vaig beure un cuiner sense mascareta, els cambrers no s'aclaraven amb els plats pero és que a més vam esperar casi 1hora a que ens portessin el menjar... no vam menjar malament pero no crec que hi torni la veritat, ah i és un lloc car.

(Translated by Google) Hello Gisela,

We apologize for the inconvenience. It was the first turn of the boy who took care of you and between the nerves and everything had some mistakes.

As for the price, I don't think we are expensive with an average ticket of € 20, below the average in Barcelona. Also, € 12-14 for a smoked Black Angus burger with a companion, all 5 of 6 are handmade by us.

Give us another chance and we will not fail.

(Original)

Disculpen-nos pels inconvenients.  Era el primer torn del noi que us va atendre i entre els nervis i tot va tenir algunes errades.

Pel que fa al preu no crec que siguem cars amb un tiquet mitjà de 20€, per sota de la mitjana a Barcelona.  A més, 12-14€ per una hamburguesa Black Angus fumada amb un acompanyant, els quals 5 de 6 són fets a mà per nosaltres.

Dóna'ns una altra oportunitat i no fallarem.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse

(Translated by Google) The incredible food, the desserts are something from another planet, I haven't eaten authentic nachos for a long time, the meats are tender and full of flavor, I think it's the best American hamburger place I've ever been to, I'll repeat as soon as I have a chance.

ATTENTION: The only thing that I can not say is the Pepsi, it is completely out of gas, I ordered 2 and we had to return them.

(Original)

ATENCION: La única cosa que no puedo decir que esta bien es la Pepsi, esta totalmente sin gas,  pedi 2 y las tuvimos que devolver.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Michael, thank you very much for your review. And thanks for commenting on the Pepsi issue.

Excuse us because we had a small problem and after you returned the Pepsis to us we realized it and we fixed it. Of course it is an isolated case and the drinks always come out normal.

Miguel, muchas gracias por tu reseña. Y gracias por comentar el tema de la Pepsi.

(Translated by Google) Sorry, and we admit the delay in 1 dish and the error in the ticket with the bottle (corrected at the moment). But the lack of education is yours.

Having looked at the menu beforehand you refused to pay for the brisket supplements, Signature Fries and drinks that were served to you.

You made the team so dizzy that it was 1:30 and you were still sitting when we closed at 00:30. If you dine in a restaurant you pay for EVERYTHING you consume,

(Original)

Habiendo mirado la carta de antemano os negabais a pagar los suplementos del Brisket, las Signature Fries y bebidas que se os sirvieron.

Tanto habeis mareado al equipo que eran la 1:30 y todavía estabais sentados, cuando cerramos a las 00:30. Si cenáis en un restaurante pagáis TODO lo que consumís,

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) It is the perfect restaurant to try American food. The decoration of the place is beautiful and done in detail to create an American atmosphere. The food is amazing and all the portions are huge. There is a lot of variety to choose from, personally the wings and the incredible nachos. But best of all, without a doubt, the service, very friendly and quick both to attend and to serve. It is the ideal place to go with family, with a partner or friends, without a doubt you have to try it! I was very happy with the experience.

(Original)

La comida está increíble y todas las raciones son contundentes. Hay mucha variedad para escoger, personalmente las alitas y los nachos increíbles. Pero lo mejor de todo sin duda el servicio, muy amables y rápidos tanto para atender como para servir. Es el sitio ideal tanto para ir con familia, con pareja o amigos, sin duda hay que probarlo! Quedé muy contenta con la experiencia.

(Translated by Google) One of the best restaurants I've been to in Barcelona, ​​just a few meters from Plaza Catalunya. The truth is that I had been told very well about this restaurant, but I wanted to know if it was as good as they said. Well let's say I just left and I'm already thinking about when to come back.

I have eaten the King Ranch hamburger and it is true that the quality of the ingredients is very noticeable and especially the Black Angus meat. Seriously, what a burger. Now I have the dilemma for when I come back if I should repeat or let myself go and try a different one.

(Original)

Yo me he cogido la hamburguesa King Ranch y es cierto que se nota muchísimo la calidad de los ingredientes y en especial de la carne Black Angus. De verdad, qué pasada de hamburguesa. Ahora tengo el dilema para cuando vuelva de si debería repetir o dejarme llevar y probar una diferente.

But it was worth it because that hamburger is incredible, I would definitely repeat it again.

totally recommended

Terminamos los entrantes y tuvimos que esperar casi tres cuartos de hora para recibir las hamburguesas (algo debió pasar porque no fue normal esa espera)

Totalmente recomendado

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We ordered the Ranch Combo as a starter and got the unpleasant surprise that the mac & cheese cubes were still frozen in the center, while the onion rings arrived soaked in oil. It speaks very badly of a restaurant that its chef and cooks do not know how to combine the temperature of the oil and the cooking time to achieve an optimal result. It is unacceptable because that is avoided by using a thermometer. Quality control is lacking in the kitchen of this restaurant. Management is also lacking, as no one came to the table to apologize.
Otherwise, the ribs and their side of BBQ beans and coleslow were very good.
The service, good. Friendly and attentive servers.

(Original)
Pedimos el Ranch Combo como entrada y recibimos la desagradable sorpresa de que los cubos de mac&cheese estaban aún congelados en el centro, mientras que los anillos de cebolla llegaron entrapados en aceite. Habla muy mal de un restaurante que su chef y cocineros no sepan combinar la temperatura del aceite y el tiempo de cocción para lograr un resultado óptimo. Es inaceptable porque eso se evita utilizando un termómetro. Falta control de calidad en la cocina de este restaurante. También falta gerencia, pues nadie vino a la mesa a disculparse.
Por lo demás, las costillas y sus acompañamientos de judías BBQ y coleslow estuvieron muy bien.
El servicio, bueno. Meseros amables y atentos.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Ignacio, excuse us for the experience, of course we will improve the quality control of our dishes. It is not something that happens to us often.

(Original)
Ignacio, disculpanos por la experiencia, desde luego mejoraremos el control de calidad de nuestros platos. No es algo que nos suela pasar a menudo.

Compared to a conventional brasserie, the place is very well set, the phenomenal treatment even came from the mother of the owners (Ana) aaatendemapersonalementit turned out to be a woman.

(Original)

Es un sitio donde la elaboración de los platos y la carne es muy minuciosa, utilizan productos de primerísima calidad y a la hora de degustarlo se nota la diferencia. name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text: I ordered the California burger with fries. Fries were dry (how can you even mess up on this?), burger was made from low quality meat (no texture, no taste). BBQ sauce has super market quality. And the description of restaurant says "made with soul", this made me laugh. In my opinion, low quality food for tourists, but the marketing concept and interior design are made very professionally.
owner_answer: Hi Alex, sorry for your bad experience. If we were a tourust restaurant we woukd be closed due Covid. Local people enjoy our food and know our work. Hope some day you can appreciate good food.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Although I don't eat meat, my experience has been good, because they have a couple of grilled vegetable dishes and they are very well done. The Veggie sandwich is a tower of different vegetables made hot, very tasty, I recommend it.
It is the typical American food restaurant, but it has a strong point, which is the good attention of the staff, very friendly and attentive at all times.
The dishes have a colorful and attractive presentation, added to a well-adjusted price.
Another advantage of this place is its location, 1 minute from Plaça Catalunya, with frequent public transport (metro, train, railway, bus), both day and night.
Oh, and with really big tables ideal for groups, celebrations and meetings.

(Original)
Tot i que jo no menjo carn, la meva experiència ha estat bona, pq tenen un parell de plats de verdures a la brasa i estan molt ben fets. El sandvitx Veggie és una torre de diferents hortalitzes fetes al caliu, molt gustós, el recomano.
És el típic restaurant de menjar americà, però té un punt fort, que és la bona atenció del personal, molt amable i atent en tot moment.
Els plats tenen una presentació colorista i atractiva, afegit a un preu ben ajustat.
Un altre avantatge d'aquest lloc és la seva ubicació, a 1 minut de la plaça Catalunya, amb molta freqüència de transport públic (metro, tren, ferrocarril, bus), tant diürna com nocturna.
Ah, i amb taules ben grans ideals per grups, celebracions i trobades.

(Original)

Also all the staff are very friendly and make you feel at home.

Recommended 100%

review_text:

The smoked ribs, it is true that they have the pink circle of the smoked, but the quality of the meat is not very good because they do not taste like anything. As for the smoked chicken, the same, without more, without the expected flavor. As for the first ones, we ordered some bacon cheese fries and that if I have to say that it was a very abundant portion

El pull pork que he comido en muchos sitios, viene la carne deshilacha con salsa mezclado, normalmente bbq. Pero esta no venía ni con salsa ni deshilachada. owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Jordi, thank you for your honest review. Of course serving the gin and tonic like this was a serious mistake for which we apologize. We take our cocktails seriously and consider, like many customers, that they are very good.

As for the combo of 3 meats, we serve a more than reasonable amount in general so that one person can finish the dish, although all customers leave food for not being able to finish it. It's about trying those 3 meats that, together with the companions, lets you boil over. If you want more ribs you can choose double or even triple rib.

I hope you can come back to give us a second chance! Thank you very much again.

(Original)
Jordi, gracias por tu sincera reseña. Desde luego servir así el gintonic fue un grave error por el cual te pedimos disculpas. Nos tomamos en serio nuestros cócteles y consideramos, al igual que muchos clientes, que son muy buenos.

En cuanto al combo de 3 carnes servimos una cantidad más que razonable en lo general para que una persona pueda terminarse el plato, aunque todos los clientes se dejan comida por no poder terminarselo. Se trata de probar esas 3 carnes que junto a los acompañantes te deja a rebentar. Si quisieras mas costillas puedes escoger doble o incluso triple de costilla.

Espero que puedas volver para darnos una segunda oportunidad! Muchas gracias de nuevo.

review_text:
(Translated by Google) After seeing the advertising on Instagram and the good reviews around here, it was clear to me. I wanted to go and try the tomahawk. I leave here the sample of my disappointment, the whole center was drier than the eye of a one-eyed man, it took more than half an hour to serve us despite the fact that at that time there were hardly any people, I could not "enjoy" the food either because there was Two photographers taking it for granted all the time, which made me very uncomfortable. Second time and there won't be a third, a real shame

(Original)
Después de ver la publicidad en Instagram y las buenas reseñaste de por aquí lo tuve claro. Quería ir y probar el tomahawk. Os dejo por aquí la muestra de mi decepción, todo el centro estaba más seco que el ojo de un tuerto, tardaron más de media hora en servirnos pese a que en ese momento apenas había gente, tampoco pude “disfrutar” de la comida porque había dos fotógrafos dando por saco todo el rato cosa que me incomodó muchísimo. Segunda vez y no habrá una tercera, una auténtica lástima
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Marta, we are very sorry for your experience. Tomahawk is a bit tricky as it is Duroc pork, not beef. It is a slightly drier meat than veal. Anyway, if it happens again (in this or another restaurant), comment your concern and change your plate.

Of course this piece had not turned out well, and we are sorry. We always try to improve and we stand up when these things happen.

(Original)
Marta, lamentamos mucho tu experiencia. El tomahawk es un poco complicado, ya que es carne de cerdo duroc, no ternera. Es una carne un poco mas seca que la de ternera. De todos modos, si volviese a ocurrir (en este u otro restaurante) comenta tu preocupación y se te cambia el plato.

Desde luego esta pieza no habia quedado bien, y lo sentimos. Tratamos siempre de mejorar y damos la cara cuando estas cosas pasan.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Do not be fooled a priori by anything. It is not another place with more or less good hamburgers. It is "the best American-style hamburger and meat restaurant in all of Barcelona". I've only tried one. And I don't need anything else. Each and every ingredient was of the highest order. They only needed to bring each one the traceability label. A Feast for the Senses. And a tribute to those of us who really enjoy things well done. With effort and love. Despite a yanky name that could invite you to think about a business without a soul for some small group of investors with excess cash, behind are Robert and his mother, both at the foot of the canyon at 6 in the afternoon. For this reason and for a superb and brutally executed product, they will be an absolute reference in this city. For ten years, I had only loved the Coure hamburger. Today, they share a well-deserved podium.

(Original)
No te dejes engañar a priori por nada. No es otro local de hamburguesas más o menos buenas. Es "el mejor restaurante de hamburguesas y carnes de estilo americano  de toda Barcelona". Sólo he probado una. Y no me hace falta nada más. Todos y cada uno de los ingredientes eran de primer orden. Solo les faltaba llevar a cada uno la etiqueta de trazabilidad. Una fiesta para los sentidos. Y un homenaje a aquellos de nosotros que disfrutamos de las cosas bien hechas de verdad. Con esfuerzo y cariño. A pesar de un nombre yanky que podría invitar a pensar en un negocio sin alma de algún grupito de inversores con exceso de cash, detrás están Robert y su madre, los dos a pie del cañón a las 6 de la tarde. Por eso y por un producto excelso y brutalmente ejecutado, serán un referente absoluto en esta ciudad. Hacia diez años que sólo me chalaba la hamburguesa del Coure. Hoy, ellos comparten merecido pòdium.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Thank you very much for your incredible review! Of course we put effort and love into everything we do, and being valued is the best in the world.

(Original)
Muchas gracias por tu increible reseña! Desde luego le ponemos esfuerzo y cariño a todo lo que hacemos, y que nos valoren es lo mejor del mundo.

The mac'n cheese are also quite good and the entrees meh, passable, neither the nachos were spectacular nor the tequeños do not stand out much.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
Downgrading my review further to a 1 star due to the terrible response from the "owner". Based on this response, they're basically saying that if you are a few minutes late; you will be punished with terrible service, a table in the cold along with cold food where they just forget about you. But folks, it gets better - don't you just love technology? Please see the Google timeline image attached which clearly shows we were never anywhere near 25 minutes late, just a few minutes - it has a logged time. But hey, maybe if you don't leave customers waiting around for someone to eventually seat them they would have actually been on time? Oh, and BTW - maybe go speak to your waiter and ask if we were "nice" or not. I'm 100% sure your waiter will disagree with you, we never blamed him for the bad experience. The poor guy was simply overwhelmed due to YOUR bad management, and got a tip from us regardless. You clearly do not have enough staff for the amount of people, and have terrible quality control, serve cold food - and clearly cannot accept criticism either by making up stories that we were 25 (or 40 min depending on your wording) minutes late?? And then you have the cheek to imply we are not nice customers because we are leaving honest feedback... Oh well....

(Original Review)
Disappointing. Made a booking for 10pm, only to arrive and find that our booking had been crossed out. We were eventually seated outside, in the cold, which we accepted and were then completely forgotten with no service to be found. To be fair the waiters did eventually come to apologize, blaming it on how busy they were and the food came exceptionally quick once ordered (in fact, looooong before our drinks - how??) but while the sides were nice and warm, the meats (pulled pork and ribs) and burgers were ice cold. An hour later and after asking various different waiters for a bill, we eventually had to get a barman to chase one down so we can pay and finally leave. Clearly a tourist trap with no regard to customer service, would recommend to avoid this place.
owner_answer: Nicholas, sorry for the misunderstanding, but we take our booking rules seriously. Wherever you go in Barcelona, more in Saturdays, if you arrive 25 minutes late on your booking (without calling beforehand) you lose your table. We can't keep people waiting with empty tables due to bookings that not arrive on time (or 15 mins later, maximum). Sure whenever people on bookings arrive too late it feels bad for us and we try hard to have a table ready or whatever we can do, but understand our position and that of the people who are waiting for a table. Next time just make a simple 1 minute call to let anyone know and extend your booking a little bit more. Thanks!

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) I was looking forward to trying The Ranch, but I think we went on a bad day, which sometimes anyone has.

We knew in advance that they did not have Brisket that day because they only do it some days of the week. We wanted to order the Tomahawks but they did not have them, as well as 5 other dishes on the menu including the Mac'N'cheese Fritos etc.

In the end I ordered the combo of several meats, the best was the ribs followed by the chicken. The Pulled Pork was good but very dry too.
I went to pour barbecue sauce from one of the glass jars, one was almost empty, it smelled of barbecue but there was only like an oil that had separated below. In the other glass jar there was but. I ordered BBQ beans with Mashed Potato as a side dish and they took out French Fries instead of the Mashed Potato.

They gave my father a crystal glass with a very important splinter that they did change and they apologized.

I say it again, sometimes a bad day can be anywhere, even my favorite restaurants, and nothing happens. And sometimes a series of things influences the general experience, Barcelona is far away and we had the Ranch on our list, so we wanted to. I hope to be able to try again in the future and that our expectations are met.

(Original)
Tenía ganas de probar The Ranch, pero creo que fuimos en un mal día, que a veces lo tiene cualquiera.

Sabíamos de antemano que ese día no tenían Brisket porque lo hacen solamente algunos días de la semana. Queríamos pedir los Tomahawks pero no les quedaban, igual que otros 5 platos de la carta incluyendo los Mac'N'cheese Fritos etc.

Al final pedí el combo de varias carnes, lo mejor fue las costillas seguido por el pollo. El Pulled Pork estaba bueno pero muy seco también.
Fui a echar salsa barbacoa de uno de los botes de cristal, uno estaba casi vacio, olía a barbacoa pero abajo solo había como un aceite que se había separado. En el otro bote de cristal sí había pero. Pedi de acompañamiento judias BBQ con Puré de Patata y me sacaron Patatas Fritas en vez del Puré.

A mi padre le dieron un vaso de cristal con un astilla bastante importante que sí lo cambiaron y pidieron disculpas.

Lo vuelvo a decir, a veces un mal día lo puede tener cualquier sitio incluso  mis restaurantes favoritos y no pasa nada.  Y a veces una serie de cosas influye en la experiencia general, Barcelona nos queda lejos y teníamos al Ranch en nuestro listado, entonces teníamos ganas. Espero poder volver a probar en un futuro y que nuestras expectativas se cumplan.

Huid de este restaurante donde solo hay extranjeros y la comida no vale absolutamente nada, ¡me lo agradeceréis! name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The ranch smokehouse.

I went a few months ago to this restaurant and the truth is that I was pleasantly surprised.

I did not expect such quantities and quality, with a reasonable price (€ 20 / € 25 per person) being in the area that it is.

Located next to Plaza Catalunya, you can enter a very beautiful and well decorated place where they serve a meat well cooked on the grill.

We ordered a mix of starters consisting of onion rings, tequeños stuffed with pulled pork, very good, some battered mac and cheese squares, which were impressive and some chicken wings in barbecue sauce.

Second, I ordered a hamburger with pulled pork and pretty good bacon. Maybe I was missing a bit of barbecue sauce, the pulled was not as tender and juicy as it should be, I think it is not a constant and it was punctual. Otherwise, the burger was pretty good.

In conclusion, a place that I would go back to without hesitation and this time I would try their grilled meats.

Note: 8.5 / 10

(Original)
The ranch smokehouse.

Fui hace unos meses atrás a este restaurante y la verdad que me sorprendió gratamente.

No me esperaba tales cantidades y calidad, con un precio razonable (20/25€ por persona) estando en la zona que está.

Situado al lado de plaza Cataluña, puedes entrar en un local muy bonito y bien decorado donde sirven una carne bien cocinada a la parrilla.

Pedimos un mix de entrantes compuesto por aros de cebolla, tequeños rellenos de pulled pork, buenísimos, unos cuadros de mac and cheese rebozados, que estaban impresionantes y unas alitas de pollo en salsa barbacoa.

De segundo, yo pedí una hamburguesa con pulled pork y bacon bastante buena. Quizás me faltó un poco de salsa barbacoa, el pulled no estaba todo lo tierno y jugoso que debería, creo que no es una constante y fue puntual. Por lo demás, la hamburguesa estaba bastante bien.

En conclusión, un sitio al que iría de vuelta sin dudarlo y esta vez probaria sus carnes a la parrilla.

Nota: 8,5/10

review_text:
A smoke house that serves non smoked beef from its smoked menu?????

In response to the comment left by the restaurant below.  I would prefer you to just say you ran out that not mention anything and serve non smoked beef when we ordered smoked??? This is false advertising and poor customer service.
owner_answer:
Hi Sarah! We smoke brisket from Thursday to Friday. It comes out by Friday night until end of existences after 24 hours of smoking. We don't do fast smoking pieces as they are low quality and the result is not that good.

So we prefer to serve brisket as an exclusive piece for a limited time rather than save time in the process and serve bas brisket that won't like anybody.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Disappointing premiere in this place ... I arrive with my partner at 10:30 p.m., we sit on the terrace and no one comes out to attend us, after ten minutes we enter and order the menu, we continue waiting and we have to get up to order dinner because also They had told us that the kitchen closed at 11pm. After 45 minutes, at 11:30 p.m. they bring us two completely incomplete hamburgers with changed ingredients to try to fill in the lack of the others, without taking into account possible allergens. They deliver them to us at the same time that the waiter regrets that the hamburgers are incomplete because they are short on staff and stocks ... because he did not notify 45 minutes before? It came with the predisposition that we would accept some type of discount to which we woke up totally disappointed. We will certainly NEVER return.

(Original)
Decepcionante estreno en este lugar...Llego con mi pareja a las 22.30h, nos sentamos en la terraza y no sale nadie a atendernos, tras diez minutos entramos y pedimos la carta, seguimos esperando y nos toca levantarnos para pedir la cena porque además nos habían comentado que a las 23h cerraban cocina. Tras 45 minutos, a las 23.30h nos traen dos hamburguesas completamente incompletas y con ingredientes cambiados para tratar de rellenar el faltante de los otros, sin tener en cuenta posibles alérgenos. Nos las entregan al mismo tiempo que el camarero lamenta que las hamburguesas estén incompletas porque van justos de personal y de existencias...porque no avisó 45minutos antes? Venía con la predisposición de que aceptaríamos algún tipo de descuento a lo que nos levantamos totalmente decepcionados. Desde luego no volveremos NUNCA.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The place was very good, the atmosphere and the perfect decoration.
I went with my partner who loves meat and we ordered the chicken wings with Jack Daniel's BBQ sauce as a starter, it was very tasty but what I did not know is that they charged you a supplement (nothing, 1 euro) for that sauce.
Then we ordered a combo of 3 meats: ribs, pulled pork and chicken fingers.
The ribs I love everywhere so perfect.
The pulled pork was very dry and for me personally it made a bit of a ball, but if you put barbecue sauce on it it was good.
And the chicken fingers left to be desired, they were a little dry and my partner said he caught some that were chewy.
Price quality is fine, maybe I'll be back, but I don't know if I was going with very high expectations.

(Original)
El sitio estaba muy bien, el ambiente y la decoración perfecto.
Fui con mi pareja que nos encanta la carne y nos pedimos de entrante las alitas de pollo con salsa BBQ de Jack Daniel's, estaba muy rica pero lo que no sabía yo es que te cobraban un suplemento (nada, 1 eurillo) por esa salsa.
Después nos pedimos un combo de 3 carnes: Costillas, pulled pork y fingers de pollo.
Las costillas a mi me encantan en todos los sitios así que perfectas.
El pulled pork estaba muy seco y a mi personalmente se me hacía un poco de bola, pero si le ponías salsa barbacoa estaba bueno.
Y los fingers de pollo dejaban que desear, estaban un poco secos y mi pareja dijo que pilló algunos que estaban chiclosos.
Calidad precio está bien, quizá vuelvo, pero no sé si iba con las espectativas muy altas.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text: It used to be good but it seems the brisket is not on the menu anymore, we ordered 2 burgers and waited 45m inside before our dishes came... The staff was nice but they could have explained why it took so long.
owner_answer:
Thanks for your comment ChrissAlbass. Sorry for your bas experiences. Please, think that some steaks and burgers can take a lot of time if they are ordered "well done". We make sure about that for you to be confortable with the point of the meat.

Also, if you came on Friday or Saturday night it use to be slower because we are full of customers.

Surely we try our best, hope you can give us a second try.

The hamburger is well knit and the flavors combine well, the Pulled Pork is super sweet.
And the treatment of the unbeatable staff. I will be back.

(Translated by Google) They had no pulled pork at noon. We went precisely for this and were disappointed. The bacon cheese fries were very average and the Mac and cheese the same. The burger I ordered was very good.
I do not understand how it is possible that he does not have one of his star dish prepared for a noon.

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) We went at noon with a great desire to try smoking since we know that very few places work this technique in Spain. We were very disappointed because the star dish pulled pork turns out that they had not prepared it, we understand that it is cooked for 12 hours and others but we were surprised that they did not have it prepared at noon. We ordered bacon cheese fries and it was a big disappointment, frozen potatoes with bag cheddar and ranch sauce from ... pot? Incredible burgers, really good, but the total computation, disappointment

(Original)
Fuimos a medio día con muchisimas ganas de probar el ahumado ya que sabemos que muy pocos sitios trabajan esta técnica en españa. Nos llevamos una gran decepcion porque el plato estrella pulled pork resulta que no lo tenían preparado, entendemos que se cocina durante 12h y demás pero nos sorprendió que no lo tuviesen preparado a medio dia.  Pedimos bacon cheese fries y fue una gran decepcion, patatas congeladas con cheddar de bolsa y salsa ranchera de... bote? Las hamburguesas increibles, realmente buenas, pero el computo total, decepción

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text: Updated: NO LONGER HAD BRISKET!! no mention of it anywhere. The screens and posters in the place still mention it but it is no longer on the menu. How can you be a Smokehouse and not have brisket. My wife and I sat there baffled for a couple of minutes and walked out.  --------- Hands down the best BBQ place in Barcelona. The Brisket was amazing as were the sausages.
owner_answer:
First of all, you just sit and leave without asking for an explanation or letting us give it. We guess it is our fault that our suppliers have closed or have run out of brisket due to this situation and it is not available until February although we do offer portions in special days as we can get some good brisket pieces, because we take care of the quality we get. The menu you saw was the second menu we have WITHOUT brisket in order to not create confusion among our customers if we don't have on the day, obviously. Thanks for coming and have a nice day.

The Ranch Team

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) Well-themed place, with a pleasant atmosphere and good treatment. Now, my partner and I went when it opened and, when we return again, we have noticed changes for the worse. The pork ribs and the pulled pork have a precooked taste and texture, they do not taste like smoked or barbecue. The servings are smaller too. I remember that before there was a lot of smoke and smell from the kitchen and now it doesn't. I get the feeling that what we have eaten was fifth range or food like what you could buy pre-cooked in a supermarket, therefore the quality-price is high. A disappointment, we will not return.

(Original)
Lugar bien tematizado, con un ambiente agradable y buen trato. Ahora bien, mi pareja y yo fuimos cuando abrió y, al volver de nuevo, hemos notado cambios a peor. El costillar de cerdo y el pulled pork tienen sabor y textura de precocinados, no sabe a ahumado o barbacoa. Las raciones son más pequeñas también. Recuerdo que antes salía mucho humo y olor de la cocina y ahora ya no. Me da la sensación que lo que hemos comido era de quinta gama o comida como la que podrías comprar precocinada en un supermercado, por tanto la calidad-precio es elevada. Una decepción, no volveremos.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Thank you for your sincere opinion Jordi. I can cordially tell you that we do everything ourselves, and we are even the manufacturers of the smokers. I'm sorry I didn't meet your expectations with the beginnings, but our methods are identical.

A greeting!
The Ranch Team

(Original)
Gracias por tu tan sincera opinión Jordi. Cordialmente puedo decirte que hacemos todo nosotros, e incluso somos los fabricantes de los ahumadores. Lamento no haber cumplido tus expectativas con los inicios, pero nuestros métodos son idénticos.

Un saludo!
The Ranch Team

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) The restaurant is a good place to eat with friends or in groups.
They offer a wide variety of American food based on the smoky flavor.
On this occasion I ordered the three meat combo which was not bad, since the value for money is worth it, but for those of us who have tried the true and authentic flavor of barbecue and American style firewood, they may be a little disappointed.
The doneness, the texture, and the quantity for the price is fine, but far from what is the real smoky flavor of the American style.
For now the most successful flavor is in Fat barbies, but at higher prices.

(Original)
El restaurante es un buen lugar para comer con amigos o en grupos.
Ofrecen una amplia variedad de comida americana basada en el sabor ahumado.
En esta ocasión yo pedí el combo de tres carnes que no estaba mal, ya que la relación calidad precio merece la pena, pero para los que hemos probado el verdadero y auténtico sabor a barbacoa y leña el estilo americano, pueden quedar un poco decepcionados.
El punto de cocción, la textura y la cantidad para el precio está bien, pero está lejos de lo que es el sabor ahumado y real del estilo americano.
Por ahora el sabor más acertado es en Fat barbies, pero a precios más elevados.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Armando, thank you for your constructive opinion. During our existence there was a point that we saw it necessary to reduce the amount of smoke in our cooking due to the "too" strong flavor that this entails. Our clients did not get used to it and there were complaints, this is real and it happened. Thus we decided to adjust. Of course, seeing your comment we will collect feedback again from our customers to gradually increase the level of the smoke again.

A greeting!
The Ranch Team

(Original)
Armando, gracias por tu opinión tan constructiva. Durante nuestra existencia hubo un punto que vimos necesario reducir la cantidad de humo en nuestras cocciones por el "demasiado" fuerte sabor que esto conlleva. Nuestros clientes no se acostumbraban y existían quejas, esto es real y pasó. De este modo decidimos ajustar. Desde luego que viendo tu comentario recogeremos feedback de nuevo de nuestros clientes para aumentar gradualmente el nivel del humo de nuevo.

Un saludo!
The Ranch Team

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) I was expecting something so great ... that the disappointment has been quite serious.

As a starter we have ordered some nachos, they were correct and the portion was generous.

Second I was with my only and absolute obsession to try the brisket that they have been promoting so much and the Pulled pork.

The first ... was not in the letter anymore. Entering a place full of posters that invite you to eat it ... and that there is no ... it is a stick. As for pulled pork, I have tried it on my hamburger. The Pulled Pork was bland, lacking in humor. I have tried many Pulled Pork in BCN and this one did not seem to me to be the best, rather just cooked meat. However, the meat of the hamburger has seemed wonderful to me. Very good. And the hamburger as a whole and with the exclusive sauces of the place entered alone.

MC and cheese have seemed like galets with a loose cheese. Let no one expect to travel to the US with their palate.

The service somewhat slow and it was difficult for him to clarify and assist you. But in his favor I will say that it was little personal for so many people. There was little else they could do and the kitchen people were there to help them out.

Anyway, I will give another chance as I have been wanting to try the ribs.

(Original)
Esperaba algo tan genial...que la decepción ha sido bastante seria.

De entrante hemos pedido unos nachos, estaban correctos y la ración era generosa.

De segundo yo iba con mi única y absoluta obsesión de probar el brisket que tanto llevan promocionando y el Pulled pork.

El primero...no estaba en carta ya. Entrar a un local lleno de carteles que te invitan a comerlo...y que no haya...pues es un palo. En cuanto al pulled pork lo he probado en mi hamburguesa. El Pulled Pork estaba soso, le faltaba gracia. He probado muchos Pulled Pork en BCN y este no me ha parecido de los mejores, más bien carne cocida sin más. Sin embargo la carne de la hamburguesa me ha parecido maravillosa. Buenísima. Y la hamburguesa en conjunto y con las salsitas exclusivas del lugar entraba sola.

Los MC and cheese me han parecido galets con un queso flojo. Que nadie se espere viajar a EEUU con el paladar.

El servicio algo lento y le costaba aclararse y atenderte. Pero en su favor diré que era poco personal para tanta gente. Poco más podían hacer y la gente de cocina estaba al quite para echarles una mano.

De todos modos, volveré a dar otra oportunidad ya que me he quedado con ganas de probar el costillar.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Thanks for your constructive criticism Martin. It is true that we are having problems with the Brisket supplier and we have few pieces this season, so we have it available on time and even out of stock for long periods.

On the other hand, our pulled pork is usually very good, I am sorry that it did not meet your expectations and I hope you give it a second chance because we will not fail twice.

A greeting!
The Ranch Team

(Original)
Gracias por tu crítica tan constructiva Martin. Es cierto que estamos teniendo problemas con el proveedor de Brisket y disponemos de pocas piezas esta temporada, por lo que lo tenemos disponible puntualmente e incluso fuera de stock durante largos periodos.

Por otro lado, nuestro pulled pork suele estar muy bien, lamento que no haya cumplido tus expectativas y espero que le des una segunda oportunidad porque no fallaremos dos veces.

Un saludo!
The Ranch Team

name: The Ranch Smokehouse
review_text:
(Translated by Google) My partner and I went by reservation. We ordered the fried Mac & cheese starter, which was macaroni and cheese in batter cubes, very good, but not suitable for low calorie diets. And for the main a combo of 3 meats with pulled pork (I was disappointed, I found it somewhat dry), chicken thigh (rich and juicy) and ribs (very good and juicy). We didn't have room for dessert.

I have to say that our first option was to order the Santa Fe Skirt and Denver Tomahawks, but they didn't fit, too bad.

Very attentive and friendly waiter.

(Original)
Fuimos mi pareja y yo con reserva. Pedimos de entrante Mac&cheese frito, que eran cubos rebozados de macarrones con queso, muy bueno, pero no apto para dietas bajas en calorías. Y de principal un combo de 3 carnes con pulled pork (me decepcionó, lo encontré algo seco), muslo de pollo (rico y jugoso) y costillas (muy buenas y jugosas). No nos quedó espacio para postre.

He de decir que nuestra primera opción era pedir Santa Fe Skirt y Denver Tomahawks, pero no les quedaban, una lástima.

Camarero muy atento y amable.
owner_answer:
(Translated by Google) Maria, thank you for your comment! I'm sorry the pulled was a little dry and we didn't have the Santa Fe Skirt or the Denver Tomahawks available. We will surely have them available next time without problem.

A greeting!
The Ranch Team

(Original)
Maria, gracias por tu comentario! Lamento que el pulled estuviera algo seco y que no tuviéramos disponibles ni la Santa Fe Skirt ni el Denver Tomahawks. Seguro la próxima los tenemos disponibles sin problema.

Un saludo!
The Ranch Team
